body:
favourite things | mcu edition

steve rogers

steve’s favourite thing about you is your smile. it’s just so contagious. every time you flash that smile, steve can’t help but smile too. there’s nothing he loves more than seeing you smile at him.

tony stark

tony’s favourite thing about you is your lips. they’re perfectly shaped to fit his. he loves how soft they are and the way they move when you talk. when you bite your lip when you concentrate, that drives him crazy.

natasha romanoff

nat’s favourite thing about you is your arms. she feels safe when your arms are around her, holding her close, protecting her. that’s where she feels most at home.

peter parker

peter’s favourite thing about you is your eyes. he gets lost just admiring the beautiful colour of your irises. he loves the way your eyes communicate how you’re feeling.

bucky barnes

bucky’s favourite thing about you is your hands. he loves holding your hands, keeping each other close. he can’t help but feel sleepy when you play with his hair while he lays on your chest.

thor odinson

thor’s favourite thing about you is your laughter. the way your laugh can make everyone else in the room laugh. he loves all of your laughs, your giggle, your hearty laugh, your chuckle.

body:

JAKARTA.bipol.co -Tahun lalu, ‘Avengers: Infinity War’ merupakan film terpanjang dalam sejarah Marvel Cinematic Universe. Namun rekor itu akan segera dipecahkan.

‘Avengers: Endgame’ disebut bakal lebih panjang dari film sebelumnya. Menurut kabar, film yang akan ditayangkan 26 April itu berdurasi tiga jam dua menit.
